Output demo.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1000
Set Height 600
Set TypingSpeed 40ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.0

Type "chat --debug"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "what files are in this directory? reply in one sentence."
Enter
Sleep 6s

Type "/calculate 2 + 3"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "/ls itest"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "/cat itest/sample.txt"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "/grep needle itest/*.txt"
Enter
Sleep 1s
